{
  "texts": [
    "The advantage of BERTopic is that it leverages the context-capturing capabilities of transformer models, which are superior to traditional techniques when it comes to understanding semantic meanings of words 61.",
    "Initially, the dataset was filtered to include only English-language comments.",
    "For language detection, we employed the xlm-roberta-base-language-detection model 62 for all platforms, with the exception of Twitter, as the raw Twitter data was already sorted by language.",
    "This model achieved an average accuracy of 99.6% on a benchmark of 20 languages 63.",
    "Next, we preprocessed the data by removing URLs and stop words to reduce noise."
  ]
}